        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Descriptive information for an arrangement or division of contractual states outlining how the employee is related to the employer, which determines their rights and their employer&apos;s responsibilities in regard to them, into groups based on criteria such as characteristics, which the objects have in common</skos:definition>
