        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">Insurance Claim Loss Cause</rdfs:label>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Specific condition, incident, or physical phenomenon that directly precipitates a physical or financial impairment to an insured asset, forming the fundamental basis for a request for contractual indemnification</skos:definition>
