        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">ECC 200</rdfs:label>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Data Matrix using Reed-Solomon codes for error and erasure recovery, supporting inverse reading symbols, specification of the character set, rectangular symbols, and linking of up to 16 symbols to encode larger amounts of data</skos:definition>
