        <owl:annotatedProperty rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition"/>
        <owl:annotatedTarget xml:lang="en">Descriptive information for an arrangement or division of perceived hues of the epidermal keratinous filaments into groups based on criteria such as characteristics, which the objects have in common, developed by Eugen Fischer and German anthropologist Karl Saller</owl:annotatedTarget>
